{"tid":1165055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊斯籣VS同婚，支持邊個","createTime":"2019-05-21T14:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T14:12:17.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"454f697f5bd079048bf2f6350bbf31540020ac55","tid":1165055,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:07:27.000Z","msg":"【香港穆斯林委員會回應國泰航空同性伴侶廣告事件】<br />\n<br />\n昨天的《南華早報》報道，機場管理局和港鐵都不批准國泰航空在機場和港鐵站內展示同性戀意識的廣告。之後，同運人士向兩機構大力施壓。今天，該報報道兩機構都撤銷了禁令。<br />\n<br />\n以下是香港穆斯林委員會（Muslim Council of Hong Kong）對事件的回應：<br />\n--------------------<br />\n嘆息， 當我們第一次聽到他們有足夠勇氣禁止它時，我們感到震驚，並希望他們不會屈服於那只在符合他們的議程時才捍衛言論自由的壓力下。<br />\n<br />\n這就是為什麼，真主是使我們滿足的，他是優美的監護者。願真主保護我們免受這種誘惑，並絕不讓我們在我們的宗教上妥協。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1427891357476203/posts/2279078789024118/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1427891357476203%2Fposts%2F2279078789024118%2F&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TYv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=2fcd1d92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1427891357476203/posts/2279078789024118/</a>"},{"pid":"1af16ed6e71137932006286c28728eb78b5d8cce","tid":1165055,"uid":249971,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"都係毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263b422668ed5deedee4656f4d8107743b30995b","tid":1165055,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"基佬有愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2ff3fedb616eddd0301ea2859598aaffbb016c","tid":1165055,"uid":66254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"蛔會繁殖<br />\n基唔會<br />\n完"}]}